info.author: Nir Aides
info.description:
rfoo (remote foo) is a fast RPC package for Python which can do 160,000
RPC calls per second on a regular PC. It includes a fast serialization module
called rfoo.marsh and a remote console called rconsole which you can use to attach to a running script to inspect and modify its state.
info.name: rfoo
info.summary: Fast RPC package for Python (and a remote console).
